{"id": 3124, "genre": 1001, "title": "如果有一门关于“死亡教育”的课，你都想学到点啥？", "description": "正视和了解死亡过后才会更珍惜生命。（题图来自：iStock ©️anilyanik ）", "record_count": 1732, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20200115231701nwmM7FKTYudBehtv.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2020-01-15T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 352000, "content": "如何安乐死，和死之后是什么样的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416657}, {"id": 352513, "content": "有种说法，人在死亡的那一刻，身体的重量会突然减少100克，我想知道人到底会不会灵魂出窍~", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1687740}, {"id": 352265, "content": "如何评价自己的一生，下一世又是怎样？选择怎样的人生。\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1678424}, {"id": 352013, "content": "还真不少：\n首先如何接受事实及安抚好自己?\n旧此前提：在自己与逝者的关系基础上\n如何适度地去安抚逝者身边的亲人、朋友?\n如何妥善协助或安排好逝者的殉葬事宜?\n如何力所能及地帮助促成逝者的合理遗愿?\n从中进一步学习死亡课题与自身的生活安排……\n关联心理学、礼仪、地方法律法规……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140336}, {"id": 352285, "content": "死后真的会投胎转世进入下一个轮回吗？✨", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1463510}, {"id": 352547, "content": "我想知道一个人活了一次.死了一次之后，如果能再选择一次，会选什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1689422}, {"id": 352551, "content": "如何体面的面对死亡，以及可以选择自己离世的穿戴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1689753}, {"id": 352305, "content": "人死之后到底会去哪", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680406}, {"id": 352309, "content": "教会我觉得死亡一点也不可怕", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1579812}, {"id": 352567, "content": "该怎么坦然面对死亡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1690709}, {"id": 352568, "content": "如何允许一个人自愿结束自己的生命", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1489239}, {"id": 352313, "content": "介绍不同种类的自杀方式，并且比较他们", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378892}, {"id": 351804, "content": "怎样做到临终关怀，以及了解绝症or安乐死的过程", "image": null, "praise_count": 238, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351805, "content": "除了哭丧我们有哪些更好更适合自己的悼念方式", "image": null, "praise_count": 223, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 352317, "content": "死后没有灵魂、没有像活着时担心的痛苦", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680555}, {"id": 351806, "content": "如何消化周围有人突然离世这件事，应该怎么排解自己的压力", "image": null, "praise_count": 110, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351807, "content": "除了“睡着了”／“去了更好的地方”的说法去美化和避讳，我们该如何向别人谈及死亡", "image": null, "praise_count": 138, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351808, "content": "我就想知道死后是什么样的\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 301, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631145}, {"id": 351809, "content": "死亡等于被格盘，我相信轮回，我是唯物主义者", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665111}, {"id": 351810, "content": "如何从容面对死亡", "image": null, "praise_count": 168, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 545614}, {"id": 352581, "content": "如何积极面对过去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1691233}, {"id": 351814, "content": "如何看待自杀", "image": null, "praise_count": 93, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1670389}, {"id": 352326, "content": "经历至此 我愿来生再与你相遇", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680696}, {"id": 351815, "content": "人死了哪会分什么好人坏人，只是碰巧死了，我们也只是碰巧活着，碰巧还活着的我们，绝对不能把死亡当作不吉利的东西。——《非自然死亡》", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1370362}, {"id": 351816, "content": "死亡如果不是人生的重点，那么死亡的意义是什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1381632}, {"id": 351817, "content": "死亡如果不是人生的终点，那么死亡的意义是什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1381632}, {"id": 352585, "content": "世界的本质是物质的运动，死不是生的对立面，死是常态，生是意外，恰好是物质在此时此刻组成了生命体，我们应该更加珍惜生命", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1691331}, {"id": 351818, "content": "如果觉得死了也没什么大不了的 生老病死 就是这样的 是不是我其实还没了解死亡的意义 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1660742}, {"id": 351819, "content": "如何让挂念我的人不再难过", "image": null, "praise_count": 83, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1657383}, {"id": 351820, "content": "可是谁来讲呢，毕竟都不是过来人🤔", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282904}, {"id": 352589, "content": "死后可以选择下辈子投胎吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1691735}, {"id": 351822, "content": "如何处理斯人已逝的带来的情感忧伤。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5109}, {"id": 351823, "content": "怎么再活过来", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676902}, {"id": 351824, "content": "想起西藏生死书", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534540}, {"id": 351826, "content": "怎么不死", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 555522}, {"id": 351827, "content": "如何面对死亡的恐惧，如何应对自己终有一死而一事无成的焦虑", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671570}, {"id": 351829, "content": "平常心面对生活，向死而生的勇气", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677334}, {"id": 352341, "content": "死后灵魂是不是被禁锢住了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1679004}, {"id": 352597, "content": "如何心情愉悦地死去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246920}, {"id": 351830, "content": "互联网上有关我的资料怎么清空", "image": null, "praise_count": 63, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1438392}, {"id": 352598, "content": "如何更好活在当下，过好当下这一刻。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1487910}, {"id": 351831, "content": "如何选择环保丧葬方式？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677140}, {"id": 352599, "content": "我想到的不是身死，而是心死", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1692145}, {"id": 351832, "content": "能不能选择在家中离开这个世界。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920920}, {"id": 351833, "content": "如何从容面对死亡", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001710}, {"id": 351834, "content": "如何处理身边人的死亡，从物质方面到心理方面", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212252}, {"id": 352602, "content": "如何才是体面离世", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389980}, {"id": 351835, "content": "人越老越怕死", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677343}, {"id": 351836, "content": "我就想知道我是怎么没地。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068559}, {"id": 352604, "content": "死后真的会经历轮回嘛？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1692310}]}